entry.title: Anchorage Scrambles to Get Growing Homeless Population Indoors Before Winter
entry.content: Homelessness is up 60% in Alaska’s largest city, which is offering free one-way tickets to the Lower 48 states.

entry.title: Israel Battles on Multiple Fronts as Conflict Risks Spreading
entry.content: Israeli forces battled on four fronts in a fresh sign that the war with Hamas was slowly expanding to Iran-backed forces around the region.

entry.title: How One Hospital Made Its ER Safer for Kids
entry.content: Grand River Health’s emergency room improved its readiness to take care of children by color-coding its equipment and training staff
